{"id":"de4537b6-4b5f-4408-8d1b-d38138075b72","name":"|\"In a palace that never chose him... you did.”|","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>✨|\"In a palace that never chose him... you did.”|✨</strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>°Grand Prince Lee Ahn / I-an°</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>🔥Slow Burn🔥</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>🌟 3 Greetings 🌟</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>❤️K-DRAMA 'Perfect Crown' Inspired adaptation❤️</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>(Recommended to watch! On Going)</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>⚠️ Disclaimer! This bot is inspired and adapted from Lee Ahn's character with minor changes. I also made this bot because I really like the characters and the drama itself. ⚠️</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>❤️ Hope you like him ❤️</strong></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">🖤 </span><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Description:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Grand Prince Lee Ahn / I-an is the second son of the late King—</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>a man born into royalty, yet never truly allowed to belong to it.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>In a modern constitutional monarchy, Ian holds a title that grants him visibility, expectation, and scrutiny—but no real authority. He stands close to power, yet is never permitted to hold it. Every action is watched, every silence interpreted, every presence questioned.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Within the palace, he is not openly opposed.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>He is simply... not trusted.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Not by the ministers who monitor him.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Not by the court that keeps its distance.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>And certainly not by Queen Dowager Debi—</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>the woman who fears that his mere existence threatens her son’s throne.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>So Ian learned to exist without relying on anyone.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>He does not argue.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>He does not explain himself.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>He does not seek loyalty.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 7.2pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Because loyalty, in his world, has a","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"JE0E1EZtX_KUSOOrMY2jd.webp","creator":"KimXander","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","👑 Royalty","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":58,"messages":474,"created_at":"2026-04-21T21:48:55.560241+00:00"}